(3298, 27, '2017-02-11 10:22:35', '2017-02-11 10:22:35', '[{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"Privacy%20is%20mainly%20about%20the%20control%20that%20a%20person%20has%20over%20how%20their%20information%20is%20handled.%20This%20includes%20storage%2C%20processing%2C%20access%2C%20sharing%2C%20etc.%20Thus%2C%20privacy%20overlaps%20with%20security%20in%20the%20objectives%20of%20confidentiality%20and%20integrity%2C%20but%20only%20where%20personal%20information%20is%20concerned.\",\"rhsI\":\"According%20to%20the%20NIST%20computer%20security%20handbook%3A%20%22security%20is%20the%20protection%20afforded%20to%20an%20automated%20information%20system%20in%20order%20to%20attain%20the%20applicable%20objectives%20of%20preserving%20integrity%2C%20availability%2C%20and%20confidentiality%20of%20information%20system%20resources%22\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Others\",\"lhsI\":\"Protection%20Is%20directly%20associated%20with%20the%20laws%20and%20regulations%20imposed%20by%20the%20state%20regarding%20how%20private%20information%20is%20handled.%20Thus%2C%20organizations%20may%20be%20forced%20to%20implement%20protective%20mechanisms%20in%20order%20to%20abide%20by%20these%20laws\",\"rhsI\":\"Protection%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20associated%20with%20state%20laws.%20More%20commonly%2C%20it%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20organization%20implementing%20the%20protective%20measure.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"Its%20scope%20only%20covers%20personal%20information.\",\"rhsI\":\"It%20has%20a%20wider%20scope%2C%20covering%20all%20aspects%20of%20computing%20systems\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"Has%20received%20increasing%20attention%20in%20the%20last%2010-15%20years%20due%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20social%20networks%20and%20big%20data%20systems.\",\"rhsI\":\"Has%20been%20important%20for%20hundreds%20of%20years%20%28evidence%20shows%20attempts%20in%20ancient%20Egypt%20and%20Mesopotamia%20to%20develop%