(3356, 25, '2017-02-18 09:18:08', '2017-02-18 09:18:08', '[{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Acronym\",\"lhsI\":\"P-TMSI%20stands%20for%20Packet%20Temporary%20Mobile%20Subscriber%20Identity.\",\"rhsI\":\"GUTI%20stands%20for%20Globally%20Unique%20Temporary%20Identity.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"In%20order%20to%20support%20the%20subscriber%20Identity%20Confidentiality%2C%20the%20SGSN%20%282G\\/3G%29%20may%20allocate%20PTMSI%20to%20visiting%20mobile%20subscribers.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EP-TMSI%20identifies%20a%20user%20between%20the%20MS%20and%20the%20SGSN.%20%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EThe%20relationship%20between%20P-TMSI%20and%20IMSI%20is%20known%20only%20in%20the%20MS%20and%20in%20the%20SGSN.\",\"rhsI\":\"Similar%20to%20P-TMSI%2C%20in%20LTE\\/EPC%20GUTI%20provides%20an%20unambigious%20identification%20of%20UE%20in%20order%20not%20to%20reveal%20the%20UE\\/user%27s%20permanent%20identity.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EIt%20is%20allocated%20via%20the%20MME%20and%20provides%20the%20identification%20of%20MME%20and%20Network%20as%20well.%26nbsp%3B\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Structure\",\"lhsI\":\"TMSI%20in%20general%20has%20only%20local%20significance%20%28i.e.%20within%20a%20VLR%20and%20the%20area%20controlled%20by%20a%20VLR%2C%20or%20within%20an%20SGSN%20and%20the%20area%20controlled%20by%20an%20SGSN%29%2C%20the%20structure%20and%20coding%20of%20it%20can%20be%20chosen%20by%20agreement%20between%20operator%20and%20manufacturer%20in%20order%20to%20meet%20local%20needs.%20%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EThe%20TMSI%20consists%20of%204%20octets.%20It%20can%20be%20coded%20using%20a%20full%20hexadecimal%20representation.\",\"rhsI\":\"GUTI%20%3D%20%26lt%3BGUMMEI%26gt%3B%26lt%3BM-TMSI%26gt%3B%20%3Cbr%20\\/%3EThe%20Globally%20Unique%20MME%20Identifier%20%28GUMMEI%29%20uniquely%20Identifies%20the%20MME%20that%20allocated%20the%20GUTI.%20%3Cbr%20\\/%3EThe%20M-TMSI%20is%20a%2032%20bit%20L%20that%20identifies%20the%20UE%20within%20the%20MME%20that%20allocat