(3409, 22, '2017-02-24 08:08:05', '2017-02-24 08:08:05', '[{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"Introduction\",\"lhsI\":\"Servers%20can%20be%20classified%20into%203%20categories%3A%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A%2012.8px%3B%22%3ERack%20Mounted%20Servers%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A%2012.8px%3B%22%3EModular%20Servers%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A%2012.8px%3B%22%3EIntegrated%20System%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3C\\/ul%3E%0ABlade%20Server%20is%20one%20type%20of%20Modular%20Servers.\",\"rhsI\":\"\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"Rack%20mounted%26nbsp%3Bservers%20are%20designed%20explicitly%20to%20function%20within%20a%20rack-based%20data%20center%20infrastructure.%20Although%20most%20rack%20mounted%20servers%20conform%20to%20the%20industry-standard%2019-%20inch%20width%2C%20some%20manufacturers%20continue%20to%20build%20rack-based%20platforms%20that%20are%20proprietary%20to%20their%20own%20measurements.\",\"rhsI\":\"A%20blade%20server%20is%20a%20modular%20device%20that%20fits%20with%20other%20blades%20%28which%20do%20not%20necessarily%20have%20to%20be%20servers%20themselves%29%20into%20a%20custom-designed%20chassis%20to%20create%20a%20fully%20functioning%20system.%20The%20chassis%20provides%20power%20and%20cooling%20provisioning%20to%20all%20blades%2C%20plus%20common%20management%20functions.%20It%20allows%26nbsp%3Beasy\\/rapid%20addition\\/replacement%20of%20a%20server.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Examples\",\"lhsI\":\"%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3EHPE%20ProLiant%26nbsp%3BDensity%20Line%20%28%3Cstrong%3EDL%3C\\/strong%3E%29%20server%20models%2C%20e.g.%20%3Cstrong%3EDL360%3C\\/strong%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3C\\/ul%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3EDell%20PowerEdge%20%3Cstrong%3ER%3C\\/strong%3E%20%28for%20Rack-mountable%29%20server%20models%2C%20e.g.%20%3Cstrong%3ER630%3C\\/strong%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3C\\/ul%3E\",\"rhsI\":\"%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A%2012.8px%3B%22%3E%26nbsp%3BHPE%20ProLiant%20Blade%20Line%20%28%3Cstrong%3EBL%3C\\/strong%3E%29%20server%20models%2C%20e%2Cg.%26nbsp%3B%3Cstrong%3EBL460c%3C\\/strong%3E%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3C\\/ul%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3EDell%20PowerEdge%20%3Cstrong%3EM%3C\\/strong%3E%26nbsp%3B%28for%20Modular%29%20server%20models%2C%20e.g.%20%3Cstrong%3EM630%3C\\/strong%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3C\\/ul%3E\"},{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"Other categories\",\"lhsI\":\"Other%20servers%27%20categories%20include%20%3Cstrong%3EIntegrated%20System%3C\\/strong%3E.%26nbsp%3BIntegrated%20systems%20are%20combinations%20of%20server%2C%20storage%20and%20network%20infrastructure%2C%20sold%20with%20management%20software%20that%20facilitates%20the%20provisioning%20and%20management%20of%20the%20combined%20unit.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EExamples%3A%20VCE%20Vblock%20%28Dell%20EMC%29\",\"rhsI\":\"\"}]', 'Answer for What is the difference between Rack-Mount Server &amp; Blade Server?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-rack-mount-server-blade-server', '', '', '2017-02-24 08:08:05', '2017-02-24 08:08:05', '', 3370, 'http://localhost/wp/dwqa-answer/answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-rack-mount-server-blade-server/', 0, 'dwqa-answer', '', 1),
(3410, 25, '2017-02-24 11:44:34', '2017-02-24 11:44:34', '<p>[{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Acrynom\",\"lhsI\":\"DPDK%20stands%20for%20%3Cstrong%3ED%3C/strong%3Eata%20%3Cstrong%3EP%3C/strong%3Elane%20%3Cstrong%3ED%3C/strong%3Eevelopment%20%3Cstrong%3EK%3C/strong%3Eit.\",\"rhsI\":\"SR-IOV%20stands%20for%20%3Cstrong%3ES%3C/strong%3Eingle-%3Cstrong%3ER%3C/strong%3Eoot%20%3Cstrong%3EI%3C/strong%3Enput/%3Cstrong%3EO%3C/strong%3Eutput%20%3Cstrong%3EV%3C/strong%3Eirtualization.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"Running%20in%20Linux%20user%20space%2C%26nbsp%3BDPDK%20is%20a%20set%20of%20libraries%20and%20drivers%20for%20fast%20packet%20processing%20designed%20to%20run%20on%20any%20processors.%26nbsp%3B%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EThese%20libraries%20can%20be%20used%20to%3A%3Cbr%20/%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%20small%3B%22%3Ereceive%20and%20send%20packets%20within%20the%20minimum%20number%20of%20CPU%20cycles%20%28usually%20less%20than%2080%20cycles%29%3C/span%3E%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3Edevelop%20fast%20packet%20capture%20algorithms%20%28tcpdump-like%29%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3Erun%20third-party%20fast%20path%20stacks%3C/li%3E%0A%3C/ul%3E\",\"rhsI\":\"The%20SRIOV%20mechanism%20virtualizes%20a%20single%20PCIe%20Ethernet%20controller%20to%20appear%20as%20multiple%20PCIe%20devices.%20%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EEach%20device%20can%20be%20directly%20assigned%20to%20an%20instance%2C%20bypassing%20the%20hypervisor%20and%20virtual%20switch%20layer.%20%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20users%20are%20able%20to%20achieve%20low%20latency%20and%20near-line%20wire%20speed.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Performance\",\"lhsI\":\"DPDK%20is%20believed%20to%20provide%20a%20better%20performance%20in%20terms%20of%20throughput%20and%20packet%20processing%20compared%20to%20native%20Open%20virtual%20Switch%20%28OVS%29.\",\"rhsI\":\"As%20per%20most%20of%20the%20latest%20researches%2C%20DPDK%2C%20Fd.IO%20%28VPP%29%2C%20enhanced%20virtual%20switches%20performance%20figures%20are%20still%20lower%20than%20the%20figures%20provided%20by%20SRIOV.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3ESRIOV%20is%20offering%20the%20most%20legacy-like%20performance%20figure%20that%27s%20why%20some%20typical%20NFV%20application%20such%20as%20Gateways%20are%20deployed%20using%20SRIOV.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Limitaitions\",\"lhsI\":\"Due%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20DPDK%20as%20a%20set%20of%20libraries%20enhancing%20the%20packet%20processing%2C%20it%20doesn%27t%20posses%20a%20special%20limitation%20compared%20to%20native%20virtual%20switches.\",\"rhsI\":\"Implementing%20SRIOV%20may%20introduce%20some%20limitations%20to%20the%20deployed%20infrastructure%20such%20as%26nbsp%3B%3Cbr%20/%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%20small%3B%22%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C/span%3ENo%20support%20for%20Live%20Migration%20for%20VMs%20using%20SRIOV.%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3ELess%20Control%20from%20DC%20SDN%20due%20the%20inability%20of%20most%20DC%20SDN%20to%26nbsp%3Bprovision%20SRIOV.%3C/li%3E%0A%3C/ul%3E\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"OpenStack Configuration Example\",\"lhsI\":\"%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A//01.org/openstack/blogs/stephenfin/2016/enabling-ovs-dpdk-openstack%22%3Ehttps%3A//01.org/openstack/blogs/stephenfin/2016/enabling-ovs-dpdk-openstack%3C/a%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A//docs.openstack.org/draft/networking-guide/config-ovs-dpdk.html%22%3Ehttps%3A//docs.openstack.org/draft/networking-guide/config-ovs-dpdk.html%3C/a%3E\",\"rhsI\":\"%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A//docs.openstack.org/draft/networking-guide/config-sriov.html%22%3Ehttps%3A//docs.openstack.org/draft/networking-guide/config-sriov.html%3C/a%3E\"}]</p>\n', 'Answer for What is the difference between DPDK &amp; SR-IOV?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-dpdk-sr-iov', '', '', '2017-02-24 11:57:12', '2017-02-24 11:57:12', '', 3393, 'http:/