(3427, 36, '2017-02-25 18:29:36', '2017-02-25 18:29:36', '<p>[{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"%3Cstrong%3EPlatform%20as%20a%20Service%20%28Pass%29-%3C/strong%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EPaaS%20is%20a%20set%20of%20tools%20and%20services%20that%20make%20coding%20and%20deploying%20applications%20faster%20and%20more%20efficient.%20Some%20are%20built%20with%20simplicity%20in%20mind%20%28for%20the%20less%20tech-savvy%20user%29%20and%20utilize%20simple%20point-and-click%20features%2C%20while%20others%20are%20more%20complex%20and%20require%20advanced%20coding%20skills.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%20PaaS%20deals%20with%20creating%20a%20framework%20for%20developers%20to%20create%20runtime%20environments%2C%20without%20focussing%20on%20the%20hardware%20used%20to%20do%20so.\",\"rhsI\":\"%3Cstrong%3ESoftware%20as%20a%20Service%20%28SaaS%29-%3C/strong%3E%3Cbr%20/%3ESaaS%20is%20software%20that%20runs%20over%20the%20Internet%20and%20can%20be%20used%20by%20businesses%20of%20all%20sizes%20in%20all%20industries.%3Cbr%20/%3EYou%20are%20provided%20with%20access%20to%20application%20softwares%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20on-demand%20softwares.%20You%20don%27t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20installation%2C%20setup%20and%20running%20of%20the%20application.%20Service%20provider%20will%20do%20that%20for%20you.%20You%20just%20have%20to%20pay%20and%20use%20it%20through%20some%20client.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Pros\",\"lhsI\":\"PaaS%20is%20growing%20quickly%20within%20the%20developer%20community.%20Being%20able%20to%20just%20get%20going%20on%20day%20one%20is%20a%20huge%20benefit.%20%3Cbr%20/%3EHowever%2C%20as%20it%20includes%20more%20technical%20aspects%2C%20businesses%20who%20lack%20an%20expert%20in%20this%20area%20should%20decide%20if%20there%20is%20a%20suitable%20alternative%2C%20or%20plan%20for%20possible%20drawbacks.\",\"rhsI\":\"Because%20of%20the%20web-based%20delivery%20model%2C%20SaaS%20reduces%20the%20need%20to%20run%20applications%20on%20individual%20computers%2C%20streamlining%20maintenance%20and%20support.%20Most%20SaaS%20offerings%20generally%20include%3A%3Cbr%20/%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3ERemote%20access%3AThe%20software%20is%20available%20through%20Internet%20login%20access%20to%20the%20software%20application%2C%20which%20allows%20users%20to%20work%20anytime%20and%20from%20anywhere.%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3EOngoing%20maintenance%3ASoftware%20upgrades%20and%20patches%20are%20typically%20completed%20by%20the%20SaaS%20provider%20instead%20of%20the%20user.%3C/li%3E%0A%3C/ul%3E\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Examples\",\"lhsI\":\"Microsoft%20Azure%2C%20IBM%20Bluemix%2C%26nbsp%3BGoogle%20App%20Engine%2C%20Apache%20Stratos.\",\"rhsI\":\"Google%20Apps%2C%20Microsoft%20Office%20365.\"}]</p>\n', 'Answer for What is the difference between PaaS &amp; SaaS?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-paas-saas', '', '', '2017-02-26 12:07:39', '2017-02-26 12:07:39', '', 3397, 'http://localhost/wp/dwqa-answer/answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-paas-saas/', 0, 'dwqa-answer', '', 0),
(3428, 22, '2017-02-25 18:45:01', '2017-02-25 18:45:01', '<p>[{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"Introduction\",\"lhsI\":\"The%20MSISDN%20together%20with%20IMSI%20are%20two%20important%20numbers%20used%20for%20identifying%20a%20mobile%20subscriber.%26nbsp%3BAs%20the%20network%20relies%20on%20these%20identities%20to%20route%20calls%20to%20subscribers%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20each%20identity%20is%20unique%20and%20correct.\",\"rhsI\":\"\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Acronym\",\"lhsI\":\"%3Cstrong%3EMSISDN%3C/strong%3E%20stands%20for%26nbsp%3B%3Cstrong%3EM%3C/strong%3Eobile%20%3Cstrong%3ES%3C/strong%3Etation%20%3Cstrong%3EI%3C/strong%3Enternational%20%3Cstrong%3ES%3C/strong%3Eubscriber%20%3Cstrong%3ED%3C/strong%3Eirectory%20%3Cstrong%3EN%3C/strong%3Eumber\",\"rhsI\":\"%3Cstrong%3EIMSI%3C/strong%3E%20stands%20for%26nbsp%3B%3Cstrong%3EI%3C/strong%3Enternational%20%3Cstrong%3EM%3C/strong%3Eobile%20%3Cstrong%3ES%3C/strong%3Eubscriber%20%3Cstrong%3EI%3C/strong%3Edentity\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"MSISDN%20is%20a%20number%20uniquely%20identifying%20a%20subscription%20in%20a%20GSM%20or%20a%20UMTS%20mobile%20network.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EThis%20is%20the%20number%20dialed%20when%20calling%20a%20mobile%20subscriber.%20As%20the%20MSISDN%20is%20the%20actual%20telephone%20number%20of%20the%20mobile%20subscriber%2C%20it%20is%20the%20only%20network%20identity%20that%20subscribers%20are%20aware%20of.%20All%20other%20network%20identities%20are%20for%20internal%20network%20use%20and%20subscribers%20do%20not%20need%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20them.\",\"rhsI\":\"The%20IMSI%20is%20a%20unique%20identity%20allocated%20to%20each%20subscriber%20that%20facilitates%20correct%20subscriber%20identification%20over%20the%20radio%20path%20and%20through%20the%20network.%20It%20is%20used%20for%20all%20signaling%20in%20the%20PLMN.%20All%20network%20related%20subscriber%20information%20is%20connected%20to%20an%20IMSI.%20The%20IMSI%20is%20stored%20in%20the%20SIM%2C%20the%20HLR%20and%20in%20the%20serving%20VLR.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Format\",\"lhsI\":\"The%20MSISDN%20follows%20the%20numbering%20plan%20defined%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A//www.itu.int/rec/T-REC-E.164/en%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%3EITU-T%20recommendation%20%3Cstrong%3EE.164%3C/strong%3E%3C/a%3E.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EMSISDN%20%3D%20CC%20+%20NDC%20+%20SN%20%28GSM-1800%20variant%29%2C%20where%3A%3Cbr%20/%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A%2012.8px%3B%22%3ECC%3A%20Country%20Code%20%281-3%20digits%29%3C/span%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A%2012.8px%3B%22%3ENDC%3A%20National%20Destination%20Code%2C%20identifies%20one%20or%20part%20of%20a%20PLMN%3C/span%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A%2012.8px%3B%22%3ESN%3A%20Subscriber%20Number%3C/span%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/li%3E%0A%3C/ul%3E%0AThe%20maximum%20length%20of%20an%20MSISDN%20is%2015%20digits%2C%20prefixes%20are%20not%20included%20%28e.g.%2C%2000%20prefixes%29.\",\"rhsI\":\"The%20IMSI%20format%20is%20described%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A//www.itu.int/rec/T-REC-E.212/en%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%3EITU-T%20recommendation%20%3Cstrong%3EE.212%3C/strong%3E%3C/a%3E.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EIMSI%20%3D%20MCC%20+%20MNC%20+%20MSIN%2C%20where%3A%3Cbr%20/%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A%2012.8px%3B%22%3EMCC%3A%20Mobile%20Country%20Code%20%283%20digits%29%3C/span%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A%2012.8px%3B%22%3EMNC%3A%20Mobile%20Network%20Code%20%282-3%20digits%29%3C/span%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A%2012.8px%3B%22%3EMSIN%3A%20Mobile%20Station%20Identification%20Number%3C/span%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/li%3E%0A%3C/ul%3E%0AThe%20IMSI%20has%20a%20maximum%20length%20of%2015%20digits.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Examples\",\"lhsI\":\"MSISDN%3A%20353871234567%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3ECC%3A%26nbsp%3B353%20%28Ireland%29%3Cbr%20/%3ENDC%3A%2087%20%28Vodafone%29%3Cbr%20/%3ESN%3A%26nbsp%3B1234567%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3ENote%3A%20full%20number%20portability%20is%20in%20use%20in%20Ireland%20so%20the%20mobile%20prefix%20is%20not%20a%20reliable%20indicator%20of%20which%20network%20the%20number%20is%20hosted%20on.\",\"rhsI\":\"IMSI%3A%20310160123456789%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EMCC%3A%20310%20%28USA%29%3Cbr%20/%3EMNC%3A%20160%20%28T-Mobile%29%3Cbr%20/%3EMSIN%3A%26nbsp%3B123456789\"}]</p>\n', 'Answer for What is the difference between MSISDN &amp; IMSI?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-msisdn-imsi', '', '', '2017-02-25 18:47:41', '2017-02-25 18:47:41', '', 3391, 'http://localhost/wp/dwqa-answer/answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-msisdn-imsi/', 0, 'dwqa-answer', '', 0);
