(3448, 36, '2017-03-01 16:47:48', '2017-03-01 16:47:48', '<p>[{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"Java%20is%20a%20general-purpose%20computer%20programming%20language.%3Cbr%20/%3EIt%26nbsp%3Blet%20application%20developers%20%22write%20once%2C%20run%20anywhere%22%20meaning%20that%20compiled%20Java%20code%20can%20run%20on%20all%20platforms%20that%20support%20Java%20without%20the%20need%20for%20recompilation%20as%26nbsp%3BJava%20applications%20are%20typically%20compiled%20to%20bytecode%20that%20can%20run%20on%20any%20Java%20virtual%20machine%20%28JVM%29%20regardless%20of%20computer%20architecture.\",\"rhsI\":\"Python%20is%20a%20high-level%20programming%20language%20for%20general-purpose%20programming.Python%20has%20a%20design%20philosophy%20which%20emphasizes%20code%20readability%20%28notably%20using%20whitespace%20indentation%20to%20delimit%20code%20blocks%20rather%20than%20curly%20braces%20or%20keywords%29%2C%20and%20a%20syntax%20which%20allows%20programmers%20to%20express%20concepts%20in%20fewer%20lines%20of%20code%20than%20possible%20in%20languages%20such%20Java.%26nbsp%3B%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"It%26nbsp%3Bis%20concurrent%2C%20class-based%20and%20object-oriented.\",\"rhsI\":\"It%20supports%20multiple%20programming%20paradigms%2C%20including%20object-oriented%2C%20imperative%2C%20functional%20programming%2C%20and%20procedural%20styles.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Implementation \",\"lhsI\":\"Oracle%20Corporation%20is%20the%20current%20owner%20of%20the%20official%20implementation%20of%20the%20Java%20SE%20platform%2C%20following%20their%20acquisition%20of%20Sun%20Microsystems%20on%20January%2027%2C%202010.%20This%20implementation%20is%20based%20on%20the%20original%20implementation%20of%20Java%20by%20Sun.\",\"rhsI\":\"Python%20is%20managed%20by%20the%20non-profit%20Python%20Software%20Foundation.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Open source ?\",\"lhsI\":\"Strictly%20speaking%2C%20No%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E1%29%20The%20full%20source%20code%20for%20Oracle%20JDK%20is%20not%20available.%20The%20JDK%20source%20code%20ZIP%20file%20only%20contains%20the%20source%20code%20for%20the%20public%20class%20library%20APIs.%20Not%20some%20of%20the%20%22internal%22%20class.%20Not%20the%20JDK%20/%20JRE%20toolchains.%20Not%20the%20JVM%20runtime%20itself%3B%20e.g.%20the%20JIT%20compiler%2C%20GC%20implementations%2C%20the%20verifier%2C%20etc.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E2%29%20For%20the%20subset%20that%20is%20available%20you%20need%20to%20accept%20an%20Oracle%20license.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E3%29%20The%20source%20code%20that%20is%20available%20says%20in%20the%20copyright%20headers%20that%20it%20is%20Oracle%20%28or%20Sun%29%20proprietary.\",\"rhsI\":\"Python%2C%20is%20open%20source%20software%20and%20has%20a%20community-based%20development%20model.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Handling Variables.\",\"lhsI\":\"Java%20forces%20you%20to%20define%20the%20type%20of%20a%20variable%20when%20you%20first%20declare%20it%20and%20will%20not%20allow%20you%20to%20change%20the%20type%20later%20in%20the%20program.%20This%20is%20known%20as%20static%20typing.\",\"rhsI\":\"Python%20allows%20you%20to%20change%20the%20type%20of%20a%20variable%2C%20for%20example%20replacing%20an%20integer%20with%20a%20string.%20This%20is%20called%20Dynamic%20typing\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Code \",\"lhsI\":\"Java%2C%20like%20most%20other%20languages%2C%20uses%20curly%20braces%20to%20define%20the%20beginning%20and%20end%20of%20each%20function%20and%20class%20definition.\",\"rhsI\":\"Python%20is%20unusual%20among%20programming%20languages%20in%20that%20it%20uses%20indentation%20to%20separate%20code%20into%20blocks.%20The%20advantage%20of%20using%20indentation%20is%20that%20it%20forces%20you%20to%20set%20your%20program%20out%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20easy%20to%20read%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20chance