(3452, 34, '2017-03-02 07:22:31', '2017-03-02 07:22:31', '<p>[{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"Menisci%20of%20the%20knee%20are%20two%20wedge-shaped%20pieces%20of%20meniscal%20cartilage%20act%20as%20%22shock%20absorbers%22%20between%20the%20bones%20of%20knee%20joint.%26nbsp%3B%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EWhen%20people%20talk%20about%20torn%20cartilage%20in%20the%20knee%2C%20they%20are%20usually%20referring%20to%20torn%20meniscus.\",\"rhsI\":\"Ligaments%20of%20the%20knee%20are%26nbsp%3Blike%20strong%20ropes%20to%20hold%20the%20bones%20together%20and%20keep%20your%20knee%20stable.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Types\",\"lhsI\":\"%3Col%3E%0A%3Cli%3ELateral%20meniscus%2C%20found%20in%20the%20outer%20aspect%20of%20the%20knee%20joint.%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3EMedial%20meniscus%2C%26nbsp%3Bfound%20in%20the%20inner%20aspect%20of%20the%20knee%20joint.%3C/li%3E%0A%3C/ol%3E\",\"rhsI\":\"%3Col%3E%0A%3Cli%3ECollateral%20ligaments%2C%20found%20on%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20knee%20joint.%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3ECruciate%20ligaments%2C%20found%20inside%20the%20knee%20joint.%20They%20cross%20each%20others%20forming%20%22X%22%20shape.%3C/li%3E%0A%3C/ol%3E\"},{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"Treatment\",\"lhsI\":\"Treatment%20for%20a%20knee%20problem%20or%20injury%20may%20include%20first%20aid%20measures%2C%20rest%2C%20bracing%2C%20physical%20therapy%2C%20medicine%2C%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20surgery.\",\"rhsI\":\"\"}]</p>\n', 'Answer for What is the difference between Meniscal Knee Injury &amp; Ligamentous Knee injury?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-meniscal-knee-injury-ligamentous-knee-injury', '', '', '2017-03-15 19:17:41', '2017-03-15 19:17:41', '', 3443, 'http://localhost/wp/dwqa-answer/answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-meniscal-knee-injury-ligamentous-knee-injury/', 0, 'dwqa-answer', '', 0),
(3454, 34, '2017-03-02 07:51:29', '2017-03-02 07:51:29', '[{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"Blood%20pressure%20means%20the%20pressure%20of%20blood%20in%20your%20arteries%20as%20it%20is%20being%20pumped%20by%20the%20heart.%3Cbr%20\\/%3EBlood%20pressure%20is%20measured%20in%20millimetres%20of%20mercury.%20Normal%20blood%20pressure%26nbsp%3B%20as%20two%20figures%2C%20for%20example%20120\\/80%20mmHg.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EThe%20first%20number%20%28120%26nbsp%3Bin%20this%20case%29%20is%20known%20as%26nbsp%3Bsystolic%20pressure%26nbsp%3B-%20pressure%20in%20the%20arteries%20when%20the%20heart%20contracts.%3Cbr%20\\/%3EThe%20second%20number%20%2880%29%20is%26nbsp%3Bdiastolic%20pressure%26nbsp%3B-%20the%20pressure%20in%20the%20arteries%20when%20the%20heart%20rests.%3Cbr%20\\/%3EIdeally%2C%20we%20should%20all%20have%20a%20blood%20pressure%20below%20120%20over%2080%20%28120\\/80%29.\",\"rhsI\":\"\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"what does it mean?\",\"lhsI\":\"High%20blood%20pressure%20occurs%26nbsp%3Bif%20the%20blood%20pressure%20readings%20are%20consistently%20140\\/90%20mmHg%2C%20or%20higher%2C%20over%20a%20number%20of%20weeks.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E\",\"rhsI\":\"A%20low%20blood%20pressure%20reading%20is%20having%20a%20level%20that%20is%2090\\/60mmHg%2C%20or%20lower.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"How does if feel like?\",\"lhsI\":\"Usually%20no%20symptoms%20or%20complains%20unless%20very%20high%2C%20it%20may%20causes%3A%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3EHeadaches%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3EVision%20problems%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3ENose%20bleeds%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3ETrouble%20breathing%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3EFits%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3C\\/ul%3E%0ABlack-outs\",\"rhsI\":\"Also%2C%20no%20symptoms%20unless%20too%20low%3A%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3EFeeling%20dizzy%2C%20light%20headed%20or%20fainting%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3EBlurred%20vision%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3EA%20rapid%20or%20irregular%20heartbeat%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3EFeeling%20nauseous%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3EConfusion%3C\\/span%3E%3C\\/li%3E%0A%3C\\/ul%3E\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"What is the danger?\",\"lhsI\":\"igh%20blood%20pressure%20puts%20extra%20strain%20on%20your%20heart%20and%20blood%20vessels.%20This%20can%20cause%20them%20to%20become%20weaker%20or%20damaged.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EHeart%3A%20high%20blood%20pressure%20can%20causeheart%20attacks.%20It%20can%20also%20cause%20heart%20failure.%3Cbr%20\\/%3EBrain%3A%20high%20blood%20pressure%20is%20a%20leading%20cause%20of%20strokes.%26nbsp%3B%3Cbr%20\\/%3EKidneys%3A%20high%20blood%20pressure%20can%20cause%20kidney%20disease.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%26nbsp%3B\",\"rhsI\":\"Having%20low%20blood%20pressure%20is%20not%20a%20cause%20for%20concern.%20However%2C%20sometimes%20your%20blood%20pressure%20can%20drop%20to%20a%20point%20where%20you%20may%20feel%20faint%20or%20dizzy.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Treatment\",\"lhsI\":\"1-%20Dietary%20changes%20including%20lo