(3455, 34, '2017-03-02 07:59:29', '2017-03-02 07:59:29', '<p>[{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"Both%20LASIK%20and%20PRK%20are%26nbsp%3Blaser%20eye%20surgeries%20designed%20to%20correct%20vision%20problems%20like%20nearsightedness%2C%20farsightedness%20and%20astigmatism.%20Photo%20refractive%20keratectomy%20%28PRK%29%20came%20before%20LASIK.\",\"rhsI\":\"Photo%20refractive%20keratectomy%20%28PRK%29%20is%20a%20type%20of%20laser%20eye%20surgery%20designed%20to%20correct%20vision%20problems%20like%20nearsightedness%2C%20farsightedness%20and%20astigmatism.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Technique\",\"lhsI\":\"In%20LASIK%2C%20the%26nbsp%3Bsurgeon%20makes%20an%20incision%20%28with%20either%20a%20laser%20or%20a%20blade%29%20in%20the%20cornea%20to%20create%20a%20flap%20of%20tissue.%20The%20flap%20of%20tissue%20is%20lifted%20so%20the%20laser%20can%20be%20applied%20to%20reshape%20the%20inner%20layers%20of%20the%20cornea.%20%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EThe%20computer-controlled%20surgical%20laser%20carefully%20reshapes%20the%20layers%20of%20the%20cornea%20to%20repair%20imperfections%20in%20curvature%20that%20lead%20to%20distorted%20vision.%20The%20corneal%20flap%20is%20then%20put%20back%20in%20place%20and%20heals%20over%20the%20reshaped%20part%20of%20the%20cornea%20in%20a%20few%20days.\",\"rhsI\":\"In%20PRK%2C%20the%20surgeon%20does%20not%20create%20a%20flap%20of%20corneal%20tissue.%20Instead%2C%20the%20outer%20layer%20of%20the%20cornea%20is%20removed%20to%20expose%20an%20area%20for%20a%20laser%20to%20reshape.\"}]</p>\n', 'Answer for What is the difference between LASIK &amp; PRK?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-lasik-prk', '', '', '2017-03-15 19:20:11', '2017-03-15 19:20:11', '', 3418, 'http://localhost/wp/dwqa-answer/answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-lasik-prk/', 0, 'dwqa-answer', '', 0),
(3457, 25, '2017-03-02 11:20:49', '2017-03-02 11:20:49', '<p>[{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"OPNFV%20stands%20for%20Open%20Platform%20for%20NFV.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EIt%20is%20a%20Linux%20Foundation%20Project%20that%20focuses%20on%20the%20development%20and%20evolution%20of%20NFV%20Components%20across%20many%20open%20source%20ecosystems%20through%20system%20level%20integration%2C%20Deployment%2C%20%26amp%3B%20testing.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EParticipation%20is%20open%20for%20companies%20and%20individuals.%20It%20currently%20holds%2051%20members%20%28companies%29%20including%20Tier1%20Telco%20Operators%20and%20market%20leader%20Software/Telco%20vendors%20with%20a%20SW%26nbsp%3Brelease%20every%206%20monthes.\",\"rhsI\":\"OpenNFV%20is%20an%20HPE%20Partner%20program%20that%20engage%20many%20vendors%20with%20HPE%20to%20provide%20a%26nbsp%3Breferenced%20backbone%20ecosystem%20for%20NFV.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EAs%20per%20the%20statement%20on%20HPE%20website%2C%20The%20HPE%20OpenNFV%20partner%20ecosystem%20gives%20communications%20service%20providers%20%28CSPs%29%20the%20ability%20to%20transition%20to%20NFV%20in%20a%20way%20that%20best%20suits%20their%20business%20needs%2C%20opening%20up%20access%20to%20independent%20software%20vendors%20%28ISVs%29%2C%20network%20equipment%20providers%20%28NEPs%29%2C%20system%20integrators%2C%20and%20service%20providers%20who%20offer%20best-of-breed%20NFV%20solutions.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Community Website\",\"lhsI\":\"https%3A//www.opnfv.org\",\"rhsI\":\"http%3A//www8.hp.com/us/en/cloud/nfv-partners-labs.html\"}]</p>\n', 'Answer for What is the difference between OPNFV &amp; OpenNFV?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-opnfv-opennfv', '', '', '2017-03-02 11:43:30', '2017-03-02 11:43:30', '', 3449, 'http://localhost/wp/dwqa-answer/answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-opnfv-opennfv/', 0, 'dwqa-answer', '', 0),
