(3488, 34, '2017-03-10 11:31:25', '2017-03-10 11:31:25', '[{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"A%20sprain%20is%20a%20stretch%20or%20tear%20in%20a%20ligament.%20Ligaments%20are%20bands%20of%20fibrous%20tissue%20that%20connect%20bones%20to%20bones%20at%20joints.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E\",\"rhsI\":\"A%20strain%20is%20also%20a%20stretch%20or%20tear%2C%20but%20it%20happens%20in%20a%20muscle%20or%20a%20tendon.%20Tendons%20link%20muscles%20to%20the%20bones.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"How does it happen?\",\"lhsI\":\"Sprains%20usually%20happen%20when%20a%20person%20falls%2C%20twists%2C%20or%20is%20hit%20in%20a%20way%20that%20forces%20the%20body%20out%20of%20its%20normal%20position.\",\"rhsI\":\"Strains%20happen%20when%26nbsp%3Bdoing%20the%20same%20motions%20over%20and%20over.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"How does it feel like?\",\"lhsI\":\"Pain%20and%20inflammation%2C%20and%20sometimes%20bruising%2C%20at%20the%20injured%20area.%20Depending%20on%20how%20bad%20the%20sprain%20or%20strain%20is%2C%20the%20pain%20may%20be%20mild%2C%20moderate%2C%20or%20severe.\",\"rhsI\":\"\"},{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"treatment\",\"lhsI\":\"Most%20people%20with%20mild%20sprains%20and%20strains%20can%20treat%20these%20injuries%20at%20home%20by%20following%20%26ldquo%3BRICE%26rdquo%3B%20therapy%3B%20rest%2C%20ice%20compresses%2C%20compression%20by%20elastic%20bands%20and%20elevation.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EFor%20more%20severe%20cases%2C%20see%20a%20doctor%2C%20who%20may%20do%20X-rays%20to%20check%20that%20you%20don%26rsquo%3Bt%20have%20a%20fracture.%20You%20may%20also%20get%20an%20MRI%20to%20check%20on%20your%20ligaments.\",\"rhsI\":\"\"}]', 'Answer for What is the difference between Muscle Sprain &amp; Muscle Strain?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-muscle-sprain-muscle-strain', '', '', '2017-03-10 11:31:25', '2017-03-10 11:31:25', '', 3420, 'http://localhost/wp/dwqa-answer/answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-muscle-spra