(3490, 22, '2017-03-11 17:42:31', '2017-03-11 17:42:31', '[{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"Introduction\",\"lhsI\":\"With%20licensed%20software%2C%20the%20customer%20purchases%20the%20%3Cstrong%3ERight%20To%20Use%20%28RTU%29%3C\\/strong%3E%20of%20the%20software%20%28also%20referred%20to%20as%20%3Cstrong%3ERoyalty%3C\\/strong%3E%20payment%29%20whereas%20the%20producer%20remains%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20software.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EThere%20are%20two%20main%20software%20licensing%20models%3B%20perpetual%20licensing%20and%20subscription-based%20licensing.%20The%20software%20licensing%20regulates%20the%20customers%26rsquo%3B%20rights%20regarding%20the%20use%20of%20features%20and%20capacity%20in%20the%20products.\",\"rhsI\":\"\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"The%20perpetual%20license%20model%20is%20the%20traditional%20license%20model.%20In%20this%20model%20the%20product%20is%20sold%20with%20a%20certain%20capacity%20for%20a%20one-time%20fee.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EAny%20additions%20to%20this%20capacity%20are%20paid%20for%20separately%20each%20time%20the%20capacity%20is%20expanded.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EPerpetual%20means%20indefinitely%20or%20forever.\",\"rhsI\":\"The%20subscription-based%20license%20model%20offers%20the%20customer%20the%20possibility%20to%20subscribe%20to%20a%20software%20purpose%20and%20functionality.%20In%20this%20model%20the%20customer%20signs%20up%20for%20a%20contract%20with%20a%20defined%20scope%20and%20capacity%20including%20the%20possibility%20to%20expand%20capacity%20and%20functionality%20during%20the%20contracted%20time.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EA%20term-based%20fee%20is%20paid%2C%20instead%20of%20a%20one-time%20fee.%20The%20term-based%20fee%20is%20based%20on%20the%20used%20capacity%20and%20the%20scope%20and%20therefore%20can%20vary%20from%20year%20to%20year.%3Cbr%20\\/%3E%3Cbr%20\\/%3EAt%20contract%20expiry%20or%20if%20the%20contract%20is%20terminated%20the%20customer%20no%20longer%20has%20the%20right%20to%20use%20the%20software%20license.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Software upgrades\",\"lhsI\":\"Purchased%20separately\",\"rhsI\":\"Integrated%20in%20fee\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Model type\",\"lhsI\":\"CapEx%20Model\",\"rhsI\":\"OpEx%20Model\"},{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"Example for software license fees\",\"lhsI\":\"%3Cimg%20style%3D%22width%3A%20100%25%3B%20height%3A%20auto%3B%22%20src%3D%22http%3A\\/\\/www.comparlo.com\\/wp\\/wp-content\\/plugins\\/custom-qa\\/images\\/blobid1489254022203.jpg%22%20alt%3D%22%22%20\\/%3E\",\"rhsI\":\"\"},{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"Related comparisons\",\"lhsI\":\"%3Ca%20href%3D%22..\\/what-is-the-difference-between-opex-capex\\/%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20OpEx%20%26amp%3B%20CapEx%3F%3C\\/a%3E\",\"rhsI\":\"\"}]', 'Answer for What is the difference between Perpetual Licensing &amp; Subscription-based Licensing?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-perpetual-licensing-subscription-based-licensing', '', '', '2017-03-11 17:42:31', '2017-03-11 17:42:31', '', 3435, 'http://localhost/wp/dwqa-answer/answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-perpetual-licensing-subscription-based-licensing/', 0, 'dwqa-answer', '', 0),
