(3543, 1, '2017-03-29 14:10:59', '2017-03-29 14:10:59', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_toggle title=\"What is Comparlo?\" css_animation=\"left-to-right\" el_id=\"1485949792556-3e04494f-463d\"]Comparlo is an online knowledge sharing platform in which everything is explained through comparisons. The idea is inspired by Quora; the most famous Q&amp;A site on the internet today.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"What is our mission?\" css_animation=\"left-to-right\" el_id=\"1485949792563-3f963d86-c2a8\"]Our mission at Comparlo is to build a database of great comparisons.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"How does it work?\" css_animation=\"left-to-right\" el_id=\"1485949792569-6aa7a5d9-de23\"]Comparlo is based on crowdsourcing. The content is obtained by and to the community. The platform aims at providing the user with all the necessary tools to create a great comparison.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"What categories are covered by Comparlo?\" css_animation=\"left-to-right\" el_id=\"1485949792575-97f473e3-3e21\"]A wide variety of categories is covered, including Technology, Business, Sports and much more. At Comparlo, we focus on encouraging people to learn more rather than consume more. Thus, comparing commercial products isn’t our prime goal.[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"Who is the team behind Comparlo?\" css_animation=\"left-to-right\" el_id=\"1483285128077-073c1c77-10c1\"]Comparlo is founded by a group of enthusiastic engineers who believe in the importance of free knowledge sharing.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3249\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/FullSizeRender-2-252x300.jpg\" alt=\"FullSizeRender (2)\" width=\"252\" height=\"300\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3049\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/favicon-300x300.png\" alt=\"favicon\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title=\"How to contact Comparlo?\" css_animation=\"left-to-right\" el_id=\"1483285127304-0b693662-0d5a\"]Bec